		<div class="post-2428 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-grief category-parental-units" id="post-2428">


<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/01/15/r-i-p-hiram-paley-1933-2012/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to R.I.P. Hiram Paley, 1933-2012">R.I.P. Hiram Paley, 1933-2012</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><div><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;"><a class="imagefield imagefield-jquery-lightbox imagefield-jquery-lightbox-300x300_width_height_scale" style="color: #990000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 3px; text-decoration: none;" title="Hiram Paley (&lt;a href=&quot;http://news-gazette.mycapture.com/mycapture/remoteimage.asp?image=http://assets.news-gazette.com/sites/all/files/images/2012/01/09/20120109-215753-pic-215872376.jpg&quot;&gt;Purchase a Print&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;/image/2012-01-10/20120109-215753-pic-215872376jpg.html&quot;&gt;More&lt;/a&gt;)" rel="lightbox" href="http://assets.news-gazette.com/sites/all/files/imagecache/lightbox_800_600_scale/images/2012/01/09/20120109-215753-pic-215872376.jpg"><img class="imagecache imagecache-300x300_width_height_scale aligncenter" style="border: 1px solid #000000;" title="20120109-215753-pic-215872376.jpg" src="http://assets.news-gazette.com/sites/all/files/imagecache/300x300_width_height_scale/images/2012/01/09/20120109-215753-pic-215872376.jpg" alt="20120109-215753-pic-215872376.jpg" width="255" height="300" /></a></span></div>
<div>Some articles about my Dad <a href="http://www.news-gazette.com/news/people/2012-01-10/life-remembered-hiram-paley-was-leading-progressive-urbana.html">here</a>, <a href="http://www.news-gazette.com/obituaries/2012-01-11/hiram-paley.html">here</a> and <a href="http://www.news-gazette.com/opinions/editorials/2012-01-12/hiram-paley.html">here</a>.</div>
<div>The passage of time is incomprehensible and very in my face this week.</div>
